Hide non-standard created entities:	{hide_non_standard_entities}
Cover dead zone width:	{cover_width_new}
Display device status change notifications:	{display_devices_changed_notify}
Device Changes:	Add **{devices_add}** devices, Remove **{devices_remove}** devices
Transformation rules change:	There are a total of **{trans_rules_count}** rules, and updated **{trans_rules_count_success}** rules
